HEADWORD: paranormal
<hw>par`a*nor"mal</hw> <pr>(p⟦acr⟧r`⟦adot⟧*n⟦ocir⟧r"m⟦ait⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>adj.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to parapsychology; pertaining to
forces or mental processes, such as extrasensory perception or
psychokinesis, outside the possibilities defined by natural or
scientific laws; <as>as, <ex>paranormal</ex> phenomena</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> psychic, psychical, parapsycholological.</syn>
